Weekly GBP Posting Engine
This playbook creates and schedules a recurring weekly Google Business Profile posting cadence designed to increase awareness of all services offered by the business. Each post highlights one service at a time, rotating through all services in a structured cycle. The system prioritizes pulling images from the Media Library and prompts the user if additional uploads or AI-generated images are required. Expected Benefits: - Increased awareness of all core services among local searchers - Stronger topical relevance signals in Google Maps - 

